The paper discusses the safety concerns related to superhuman artificial intelligence and the need for precise formulation of its objectives, which falls under the domain of software engineering (cs.SE) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also highlights the need for understanding the wishes and needs of a superintelligence, which involves human-computer interaction (cs.HC) and cybersecurity (cs.CY). Additionally, the paper discusses the potential risks associated with superintelligence, which falls under the domain of computer security (cs.CR).
